This paper deals with the axiomatization of logic functions based on majority operators, which is a topic related to logic and computation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). The paper also discusses circuit optimization and Boolean satisfiability, which are related to algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and computational complexity (cs.CC). Additionally, the paper mentions computer logic applications, which could fall under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) or programming languages (cs.PL).
